    "Figure 9 also demonstrates that the contribution of viscous stress to total stress diminishes with increasing wind speed.",
    "These features, which are of paramount importance from a dynamic perspective, pose formidable challenges when it comes to accurate measurement in either laboratory environments or full-scale field settings, as well as reproduction through physics-based numerical simulations.",
